@page "/spinners"
<h3>Spinner Component</h3>

<h4>Default Spinner</h4>
<p>This is a spinner with the default properties and styles.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner />
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Label (optional)</h4>
<p>The spinner component can also display an optional label if it is provided as a parameter.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Label="Loading..." /&gt;</code></pre>
<div style="width: 56px">
    <Spinner Label="Loading..." />
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With LabelPlacement</h4>
<p>The spinner component allows you to place the label in four different positions:</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Label="Top..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Top /&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Top..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Top />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Bottom..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Bottom />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Left..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Left />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Label="Right..." LabelPlacement=Placement.Right />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner Visibility</h4>
<p>This is a spinner that allows changing of the IsVisible property to show and hide the spinner.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner IsVisible=@this._spinnerVisible /&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" @onclick="ToggleSpinnerVisibility">
            Toggle Visibility
        </button>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner IsVisible=@this._spinnerVisible />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Color Parameters</h4>
<p>The spinner component also allows for simple customizations via component parameter: Color and SecondaryColor.
   Color is the spinner's foreground color. 
   SecondaryColor is only supported for a few spinners (Ring, DualRing, and Hourglass) to allow a background color change.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Type=SpinType.DualRing Color="green" SecondaryColor="yellow" /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner Type=SpinType.DualRing Color="green" SecondaryColor="yellow" />
<hr />

<h4>Spinner Type</h4>
<p>The Spinner component has different types of displays:</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner Type=SpinType.Pulse Label="Pulse" style="color: green" /&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Ring Label="Ring" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Pulse Label="Pulse" style="color: green" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Square Label="Square" style="color: darkorange" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Hourglass Label="Hourglass" style="color: darkgray" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.DualRing Label="Dual Ring" style="color: lightblue" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.SpinIOS Label="iOS Spinner" style="color: purple" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Ripple Label="Ripple" style="color: blue" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Roller Label="Roller" style="color: darkgreen" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Circle Label="Circle" style="color: red" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Blocks Label="Blocks" style="color: gray" />
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <Spinner Type=SpinType.Ellipsis Label="Ellipsis" style="color: orange" />
    </div>
</div>
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Styles</h4>
<p>This is a spinner where styles are defined: color: red; height:120 px; width: 120px.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner style="color: red; height: 120px; width: 120px" /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner style="color: red; height: 120px; width: 120px" />
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Id CSS</h4>
<p>This is a spinner with a class based on element id. The CSS element changes several properties of the spinner component.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;Spinner id="my-spinner" /&gt;</code></pre>
<Spinner id="my-spinner" />
<hr />

<h4>Spinner With Additional Classes</h4>
<p>This is a spinner with an additional class name. The CSS element changes several properties of the spinner component.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;div class="my-custom-spinner"&gt;&lt;Spinner class="my-custom-spinner"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
<div class="my-custom-spinner"><Spinner class="my-custom-spinner"/></div>
<hr />

@code {
    bool _spinnerVisible = true;

    private void ToggleSpinnerVisibility()
    {
        this._spinnerVisible = !this._spinnerVisible;
    }
}
